<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 12. C. alyciae sp. n. holotype male (MZB Cru 4672) A dorsal view of carapace B scaphocerite C dorsal view of left chelae D ventral view of left chelae. Scale bars: 10 mm (A, C, D), 5 mm (B)." , "Figure 17. Unnamed Creek, Boven Digoel Regency, habitat of the new species." , "Figure 1. Cherax mosessalossa sp. n. A holotype male (MZB Cru 4675) from Klademak Creek, Sorong City B idem, side view." , "Figure 11. C. alyciae sp. n. holotype male (MZB Cru 4672). Scale bar: 10 mm." , "Figure 10. C. alyciae sp. n. A holotype male (MZB Cru 4672) from nameless creek, Boven Digoel Regency B idem, colour variation." , "Figure 19. Phylogenetic relationships of Cherax mosessalossa sp. n. and C. alyciae sp. n. within the northern New Guinea Cherax lineage, reconstructed by BI analyses of two mitochondrial gene fragments. Number on branches show, from top, Bayesian posterior probabilities (> 0.7) and ML / MP bootstrap values (> 50). An asterisk indicates nodes with full support (1 / 100 / 100) in all analyses. The scale bar indicates the substitution rate. See Table 1 for information on the sequenced specimens. A Topology based on concatenated COI and 16 S dataset B Topology based on COI dataset C Topology based on 16 S dataset." , "Figure 13. C. alyciae sp. n. holotype male (MZB Cru 4672), dorsal view of cephalothorax. Scale bar: 10 mm." , "Figure 15. C. alyciae sp. n. allotype female (MZB Cru 4673). Scale bar: 10 mm." , "Figure 16. Dorsal view chelae. A Cherax peknyi, holotype male (QMW 28267) B C. alyciae sp. n. holotype male (MZB Cru 4672) ventral view chelae C Cherax peknyi, holotype male, (QMW 28267) D C. alyciae sp. n. holotype male (MZB Cru 4672)." , "Figure 14. C. alyciae sp. n. holotype male (MZB Cru 4672) A left first chela, dorsal aspect B left first chela, ventral aspect. Scale bars: 10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211982" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211985" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211980" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211989" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211983" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211979" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211984" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211969" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211987" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/211981" .

